data.description: AMAZING NEW PRICE!  LIKE NEW!  This is The Elm Floorplan.  This single-family home offers everything you could want and more. Enter through the foyer to the wide-open flex space and great room, which flows seamlessly to the dining space and gourmet kitchen with large island. The 2-car garage offers ample storage space. Upstairs, 4 bedrooms, a full dual vanity bath and a loft provide all the room you need – or turn the loft into a 5th bedroom. The luxury owner's bedroom boasts 2 walk-in closets and an en suite bath with double vanity with an oversized shower. This home has it all.
